dublinCore.dc:title: 119 HRES 312 RH: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Fourteenth Congressional District of Florida.

action.action-desc: Mr. Steil, from the Committee on House Administration, reported the following resolution; which was referred to the House Calendar and ordered to be printed

form.official-title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Fourteenth Congressional District of Florida.

section.text: That the election contest filed on January 9, 2025, relating to the office of Representative from the Fourteenth Congressional District of Florida is dismissed on the grounds of untimely filing with the House of Representatives.

endorsement.action-desc: Referred to the House Calendar and ordered to be printed
